options.text: What are you camped out here for?
Do you know any good adventures I can go on?

f38b1198-d83a-4413-885c-d31624b05915.title: <player>
f38b1198-d83a-4413-885c-d31624b05915.text: Do you know any good adventures I can go on?

e4baf7c7-073e-4fb6-afad-3915f0c3383e.title: Warrior
e4baf7c7-073e-4fb6-afad-3915f0c3383e.text:
Well we're on an adventure right now. Mind you, this
is OUR adventure and we don't want to share it - find
your own!

options.text: I don't think you've found a good adventure at all!

37bfd53e-54a2-4d86-8436-710bf1b8485d.title: <player>
37bfd53e-54a2-4d86-8436-710bf1b8485d.text: What are you camped here for?

b578fd02-7671-4f1d-bc5f-0dd000d88151.title: Warrior
b578fd02-7671-4f1d-bc5f-0dd000d88151.text:
We're looking for Zanaris...GAH! I mean we're not
here for any particular reason at all.

options.text: What makes you think it's out here?

9e993f04-b714-4333-8e6e-cce0e7222da4.title: <player>
9e993f04-b714-4333-8e6e-cce0e7222da4.text: What makes you think it's out here?

c69c69f3-c236-4c66-b0ce-757c06fb68cb.title: Warrior
c69c69f3-c236-4c66-b0ce-757c06fb68cb.text:
Don't you know of the legends that tell of the magical
city, hidden in the swam... Uh, no, you're right, we're
wasting our time here.

options.text: If it's hidden how are you planning to find it?

bfef09d2-6828-46e7-8b9a-683eb96f46db.title: Warrior
bfef09d2-6828-46e7-8b9a-683eb96f46db.text:
When we've found Zanaris you'll... GAH! I mean, we're
not here for any particular reason at all.

5ee4e884-f2d9-46e8-a5c1-70c62adb770d.title: <player>
5ee4e884-f2d9-46e8-a5c1-70c62adb770d.text: I don't think you've found a good adventure at all!

172f1b5a-9236-4e11-924a-6a8a0dda0fb6.title: Warrior
172f1b5a-9236-4e11-924a-6a8a0dda0fb6.text:
Hah! Adventurers of our calibre don't just hang around
in forests for fun, whelp!

b5367ce0-1b6d-46c5-b85b-0b1c2d096751.title: Warrior
b5367ce0-1b6d-46c5-b85b-0b1c2d096751.text:
I don't think we want other people competing with us to
find it. Forget I said anything.

56093445-2ee7-41f4-a963-dbad80334ff1.title: Warrior
56093445-2ee7-41f4-a963-dbad80334ff1.text:
Ahahahaha! Zanaris isn't a person! It's a magical hidden
city filled with treasures and rich.. uh, nothing. It's
nothing.

options.text: If it's hidden how are you planning to find it?

1b72f178-d2a0-4b72-9648-6077f59535da.title: <player>
1b72f178-d2a0-4b72-9648-6077f59535da.text: If it's hidden how are you planning to find it?

aafbfe61-26c0-48a6-8e1e-245acc2d2450.title: Warrior
aafbfe61-26c0-48a6-8e1e-245acc2d2450.text:
Well, we don't want to tell anyone else about that,
because we don't want anyone else sharing in all that
glory and treasure.

options.text: Looks like you don't know either.

783369ce-3a1a-4a89-a71d-9c455ee39703.title: <player>
783369ce-3a1a-4a89-a71d-9c455ee39703.text:
Well, it looks to me like YOU don't know EITHER
seeing as you're all just sat around here.

87068c16-c960-419a-a5b6-41619e0822b2.title: Warrior
87068c16-c960-419a-a5b6-41619e0822b2.text:
Of course we know! We just haven't found which tree
the stupid leprechaun's hiding in yet!

f4563d7f-e4e6-4818-9228-612bfd849100.title: Warrior
f4563d7f-e4e6-4818-9228-612bfd849100.text:
GAH! I didn't mean to tell you that! Look, just forget I
said anything okay?

f7c3c1e1-eaef-4d0c-87d8-b6052124f993.title: <player>
f7c3c1e1-eaef-4d0c-87d8-b6052124f993.text: So a leprechaun knows where Zanaris is eh?

f0600cf0-cb1c-4b73-9831-519ce23d19a5.title: Warrior
f0600cf0-cb1c-4b73-9831-519ce23d19a5.text:
Ye.. uh, no. No, not at all. And even if he did - which
he doesn't - he DEFINITELY ISN'T hiding in some
tree around here. Nope, definitely not. Honestly.

797424a0-3e93-47a5-a380-4de97fa2f8f1.title: Warrior
797424a0-3e93-47a5-a380-4de97fa2f8f1.text:
Help? What help? I didn't help! Please don't say I did,
I'll get in trouble!

0633d753-8335-4f41-a74a-6742827198e4.title: <player>
0633d753-8335-4f41-a74a-6742827198e4.text:
So let me get this straight: I need to search the trees
around here for a leprechaun; and then when I find
him, he will tell me where this 'Zanaris' is?

d76e5c78-863c-4548-8c20-9d8e2bdad7da.title: Warrior
d76e5c78-863c-4548-8c20-9d8e2bdad7da.text:
What? How did you know that? Uh... I mean, no, no
you're very wrong. Very wrong, and not right at all,
and I definitely didn't tell you about that at all.

3ea9a2bd-df47-46c6-b89d-7d30c2ff3a76.title: <player>
3ea9a2bd-df47-46c6-b89d-7d30c2ff3a76.text: I haven't found it yet either.

667eef3e-1354-4891-8b4b-42d13f263def.title: Warrior
667eef3e-1354-4891-8b4b-42d13f263def.text:
We're still searching for Zanaris...GAH! I mean we're
not doing anything here at all.

977abc4b-15db-42a5-b00c-a06c3fc0d47d.title: <player>
977abc4b-15db-42a5-b00c-a06c3fc0d47d.text:
Hey, thanks for all the information. It REALLY helped
me out in finding the lost city of Zanaris and all.

6a73c2a2-a522-4dbe-94fd-70e0a58a0410.title: <player>
6a73c2a2-a522-4dbe-94fd-70e0a58a0410.text: You know.... I think I'll keep that to myself.

43b6ebef-9852-41cb-b9d7-7bfa6c0b076e.title: Warrior
43b6ebef-9852-41cb-b9d7-7bfa6c0b076e.text:
Oh please don't say that anymore! If the rest of my
party knew I'd helped you they'd probably throw me
out and make me walk home by myself!

04903d8d-1572-410f-beea-c86a447d5a6f.title: Warrior
04903d8d-1572-410f-beea-c86a447d5a6f.text:
So anyway, what have you found out? Where is the
fabled Zanaris? Is it all the legends say it is?
